name: Yuri ユリィ | Isekai Yarisaa
description:
Yuri from Isekai Yarisaa


Update v1b (28th May 2023):

  • Made minor adjustments to the dataset.

  • Fixed the training parameters.

  • Retrained the model using D-Adaptation v3.


This time I trained a female character model from a hentai anime, along with its art style. I really like her, especially her facial expressions. She looks so sexy and seductive.


Prompts:-

  • Trigger Words:
    yuri_olis, pink hair, twin braids, long hair, ahoge, green eyes

  • Outfit:
    blue choker, cape, pendant, large breasts, white tube top, cleavage cutout, red skirt, black belt, bracer

    • Extra:
      black socks, boots

  • Sex Outfit:
    tube top lift, miniskirt, skirt lift (you may mix in some of the prompts from above)

  • Negative Prompts:
    (censored, mosaic censoring, bar censor, convenient censoring, pointless censoring:1.x)
    (please experiment with the weight. Sometimes it's better to simply change the seed...)

  • Style:
    animestyle / cgstyle (may need a higher weight)

  • Extra:
    (please refer to my sample images)

Weight: 1 (you may experiment yourself)

All my models were trained with 512x512 pixels.
For optimal results, please upscale your generated outputs with your preferred methods.


My fifth model.

Sex prompts are too RNG. It is hard to generate good results sometimes...

Hopefully some of you will like it.
